snippet.title: 😺Cats on Duty - Announcement Trailer [ESRB]😺
snippet.description:
Cats on Duty is a purr-fect blend of RTS, tower defense and match-3 mechanics. Manage two game fields at once, arm and upgrade your cat towers to defeat hordes of formidable foes. Enjoy the meow-nificent battle!

Wishlist on #Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2447260/Cats_on_Duty/

#playstation #xbox #nintendoswitch
